SELECT
                        path,
                        script_path,
                        is_flow,
                        route_path,
                        authentication_resource_path,
                        workspace_id,
                        request_type AS "request_type: _",
                        authentication_method  AS "authentication_method: _",
                        edited_by,
                        email,
                        static_asset_config AS "static_asset_config: _",
                        wrap_body,
                        raw_string,
                        workspaced_route,
                        is_static_website,
                        error_handler_path,
                        error_handler_args as "error_handler_args: _",
                        retry as "retry: _",
                        active_mode
                    FROM
                        http_trigger
                    WHERE
                        http_method = $1

SELECT
                        path,
                        script_path,
                        is_flow,
                        route_path,
                        authentication_resource_path,
                        workspace_id,
                        request_type AS "request_type: _",
                        authentication_method  AS "authentication_method: _",
                        edited_by,
                        email,
                        static_asset_config AS "static_asset_config: _",
                        wrap_body,
                        raw_string,
                        workspaced_route,
                        is_static_website,
                        error_handler_path,
                        error_handler_args as "error_handler_args: _",
                        retry as "retry: _"
                    FROM
                        http_trigger
                    WHERE
                        http_method = $1 AND
                        enabled is TRUE
